            <div class="d-block" style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: .5rem .5rem;color: var(--bs-table-color-state,var(--bs-table-color-type,var(--bs-table-color)));background-color: var(--bs-table-bg);border-bottom-width: var(--bs-border-width);box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 9999px var(--bs-table-bg-state,var(--bs-table-bg-type,var(--bs-table-accent-bg)));border-width: 0 var(--bs-border-width);display: block!important;"><label class="form-check-label" style="box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;"> 3. <b style="box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;">With minimal
                        exertion</b> (for example, while eating, talking, or performing other ADLs) or with
                    agitation</label></div>
            <div class="d-block" style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: .5rem .5rem;color: var(--bs-table-color-state,var(--bs-table-color-type,var(--bs-table-color)));background-color: var(--bs-table-bg);border-bottom-width: var(--bs-border-width);box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 9999px var(--bs-table-bg-state,var(--bs-table-bg-type,var(--bs-table-accent-bg)));border-width: 0 var(--bs-border-width);display: block!important;"><label class="form-check-label" style="box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;"> 4. <b style="box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;">At rest</b>
                    (during day or night)</label></div>
        </td>
